window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Magnus and Kaitlyn have more power than ever, but they have been warned -<i> it will come at a cost</i>.</p> <p>Vessels are missing, deals have been struck, people are unaccounted for, and time threatens to unravel. </p> <p>A contemporary romance with a dash of history and a bit of sci-fi, <i>The Wellspring</i> is the 12th book in the Kaitlyn and the Highlander series.</p> <p>If you love mysterious heroes with desperate hearts and romantic thoughts, heroines with courage who are also very ordinary disasters, and love stories that encompass all time, then you’ll love this suspenseful series. Join the adventure, buy book one today.</p>"; 
